  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个数据同步的流程图，核心是两个存储：一个是加密的Vault，存在磁盘上，用sqlite文件；另一个是工作用的stordb，可以是内存或者本地副本。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Vault",
        "stordb",
        "vault_db.sqlite",
        "stordb_db.sqlite"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。Vault是加密持久化存储，stordb是工作副本。那它们之间的同步关系是双向的吗？还是单向的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Vault",
        "stordb",
        "sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是双向同步，但stordb自己内部还有CRUD和merge操作。另外我想加一条虚线表示可以直接对Vault做操作，不过这是备选路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "stordb",
        "Vault",
        "CRUD/merge",
        "sync",
        "direct ops"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把两个节点画出来，标注好各自的存储特性。Vault用紫色填充，stordb用蓝色填充，这样视觉上能区分开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Vault",
        "stordb",
        "vaultStyle",
        "stordbStyle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "颜色区分可以，stroke宽度保持2px就行。等等，stordb到自身的CRUD/merge箭头，你画的是实线还是虚线？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "stordb",
        "CRUD/merge",
        "stroke"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "我检查了一下，stordb自环的CRUD/merge用了实线，但双向sync也是实线，这样容易混淆。我把自环保持实线，sync用实线双向箭头，direct ops用虚线，这样层次就清楚了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "stordb",
        "CRUD/merge",
        "sync",
        "direct ops",
        "stroke"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对，direct ops是虚线，表示这是绕过同步机制的直接操作。最后确认一下图例：vaultStyle是fill #f9f，stordbStyle是fill #bbf，stroke都是#333。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "vaultStyle",
        "stordbStyle",
        "fill",
        "stroke"
